    62тЖТ  debug?: boolean;
    63тЖТ
    64тЖТ  /**
    65тЖТ   * Default: `false`
    66тЖТ   *
    67тЖТ   * Override any environment variables that have already been set on your machine with values from your .env file.
    68тЖТ   *
    69тЖТ   * example: `require('dotenv').config({ override: true })`
